| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-3565 — Mass File Rename (funksec)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 1bb1097a-0bdb-533a-b579-eaff47330980"
index=*
| where (file_path="*.encrypted" OR file_path="*.locked" OR file_path="*.ransom")
